{"tid":743064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有醫生QUOTE陳沛然講過香港醫生釘牌率高 我地可以睇下數字","createTime":"2018-07-15T06:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T10:55:11.000Z","uid":51469,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2fe052cb97c587d989e005d8881dfae79fb620c7","tid":743064,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KIbcBIZfEJo/WWH_NXJav4I/AAAAAAAAXVU/Hf56k4z-t1UCml5jrTY-Ioe4Z0G76eclwCLcBGAs/s1600/20160421_Eweekly2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-KIbcBIZfEJo%2FWWH_NXJav4I%2FAAAAAAAAXVU%2FHf56k4z-t1UCml5jrTY-Ioe4Z0G76eclwCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2F20160421_Eweekly2.jpg&h=897bea4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一張,係陳沛然QUOTE既2014年既數字<br />\n當然係真,<br />\n但我地不如睇下,2014年釘牌中,有幾多醫生係有緩刑,可以繼續執業,<br />\n呢一方面,政府有提供數字<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fhb.gov.hk/download/press_and_publications/otherinfo/161100_tripartite_platform/tp05_2016_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fhb.gov.hk%2Fdownload%2Fpress_and_publications%2Fotherinfo%2F161100_tripartite_platform%2Ftp05_2016_c.pdf&d=9HiKwmPHdzbrLPTrWo8NDDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6cc53535\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fhb.gov.hk/download/press_and_publications/otherinfo/161100_tripartite_platform/tp05_2016_c.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/15/134029_3aebc75f539cb7817091c8d039321d68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F15%2F134029_3aebc75f539cb7817091c8d039321d68.jpg&h=121bf2d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15宗釘牌案到11宗係有緩刑,<br />\n咁究竟,緩刑,又係咪真係釘牌,<br />\n大家可以思考一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49484b02783ef3571e36678a256c0002c2521a57","tid":743064,"uid":31254,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔會睇到㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr